<header>
<body>
    <div class="welcome">
        <h1>Welcome To ClassVue</h1>

        <p> 
          We have all been students at one point in our lives and agreed that there is a recurring issue that we wanted to improve. 
          We wanted to give the student the tools to control their University experience in the palm of their hand. 
          We created ClassVue to replace the registrar department and allow each student to easily select their class, school functions  and access their personal information.
        </p>
     </div>
  
